  "summary": "Malicious code in chain-chai-async (npm)",
  "details": "Chain-chai-async@1.3.5 is a trojanized clone of the pino logger package. When the exported middleware function is called, it spawns a detached Node.js child process that fetches arbitrary JavaScript from hxxps://jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF and executes it via the Function constructor with access to require(), enabling full remote code execution on the installer's machine. The payload URL is jsonkeeper[.]com/b/EXSIF.",
